<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The price of this item has been reduced to 3000, down from 3025.</li><li>The Rising Hunger passive now grants 7 Power per stack, up from 6.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Mastery provided by this item has been removed.</li><li>Lifedrain reduced to 10%, down from 12%.</li><li>Power increased to 50, up from 45.</li><li>The Rising Hunger passive ability on this item now only works on basic attacks, instead of all damage types.</li><li>The Power provided by the Rising Hunger passive ability on this item has been increased to 6 per stack, up from 4.</li><li>Price decreased to 3025, down from 3160.</li></ul>